  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Ambassadors Bellevue</strong> has a great position overlooking the Bay of Naples and offers a varied menu of creative dishes made by skilled chefs.</p>
<p><strong>Restaurant Le Muse</strong> serves local specialties and international cuisine in a lovely setting with sea views. It’s open for breakfast and dinner for half board guests. Breakfast is buffet style and served between 7am and 10am. </p>
<p><strong>Snack Bar Dioniso</strong> is located next to the pool and serves grilled meats and refreshing drinks from 12pm – 5pm.</p>
<p><strong>Snack Bar Poseidon</strong> is next to the hotel’s bathing platform and has a cosy and casual atmosphere with tables right on the seafront. It’s open 10.30am – 6pm.</p>
<p><strong>Bar Afrodite</strong> serves delicious cocktails and local wines that can be enjoyed in the elegant lounge or on the patio amongst the gardens.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
