  <listingDescription><![CDATA[<p>This hotel is just ten minutes' walk from central Sorrento and has a peaceful clifftop position surrounded by a beautiful park. With fantastic service and facilities including a swimming pool, spa, bathing platform with access to the sea and some great restaurants, you'll have all you need for a five-star holiday in Sorrento. </p>]]></listingDescription>
