  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Double Partial Sea View Rooms </strong>are about 25m² and furnished in a typical Neapolitan style with a balcony and partial sea views. Facilities include air conditioning, TV, minibar, free Wi-Fi, safe, tea and coffee making facilities and a hairdryer. They can sleep up to three people.</p>
<p><span><strong>Double Garden View Rooms </strong>are about 20-28m² and have a balcony overlooking the park. They can sleep two people and are available on request, please call to book. </span></p>
<p><strong>Deluxe Junior Suites </strong>are about 37-40<span>m² and </span>sleep up to three people. They have beautiful views across the bay of Naples and Mount Vesuvius and are available on request, please call to book. </p>
<p><strong>Sorrento Suites </strong>are about 45-56m² and sleep up to three people with sea and garden views. They have a luxurious Mediterranean design with a living room and sleeping area. These rooms are available on request, please call to book.</p>]]></roomsDescription>
